channel.title: Need help portforwarding with xfinity [Have Teamviewer]
channel.description:
Hey Moparscape, I was wondering if somebody could help me with getting my server online! Im currently running a matrix 718. I have teamviewer and no-ip DUC. My xfinity has the portforwarding option on the advanced setting and everything I just need help getting it all worked out! Comment below and I will PM you my user id and password for teamviewer! thank you so much:)
[IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/3445z0n.jpg[/img]

item.title: Need help portforwarding with xfinity [Have Teamviewer]
item.dc:creator: @doom_j doom_j
item.description:
@doom_j wrote:

all you need to do is get the ip of your computer, the starting and ending port will just be 43594.

You should be able to get your ip from the connected devices tab.
